What are the cost and expenses to operate the business model?

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
One of the interest thing things about cost is it's not just the obvious ones

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.000
like people or buildings or materials.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:22.000
What you are going to be asking is what are the entire cost to operate a business model.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:27.000
You want to think about our what are the most important cost you need to worry about?

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:30.000
What are the most expensive resources you're going to need to pay for?

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.000
And what key activities are the most expensive?

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:36.000
And then you want to ask the typical accounting things.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.000
What are fix cost? What are variable cost? Are their economies of scale?

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:44.000
And you want to start getting a good handle on what it is

00:00:44.000 --> 99:59:59.000
